{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/High_octane_dark_fantasy_action_.png?t=1737993568\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture into the treacherous depths of Hell's Vestibule. Gun down the myriad monstrosities that populate Hell's corridors as you expand your repertoire. Master spells, sigils and firearms alike as you advance through this <strong>dark fantasy roguelike.</strong> \u2028</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/Flashy_gameplay.gif?t=1737993568\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/Spellcasting_fused_with_gunplay_.png?t=1737993568\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlike typical action fantasy, your spells do not act standalone. Instead, spells empowers your firearm. Your bullets <strong>are your Spell's effects.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Empty magazines full of fire bolts, turn corpses to explosions, or engrave Rituals unto the ground. <strong>Tread the illimitable road of Ritualism.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/Spellcasting_with_guns.gif?t=1737993568\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/Generate_mana_with_bullets_.png?t=1737993568\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With each bullet that strikes true, your skill is rewarded with <strong>Mana.</strong> With each Spell cast, your battle efficiency and survivability rises.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The seamless integration of spellcasting with fast-paced gunplay creates a dynamic combat system that demands quick thinking and precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/Gain_mana_by_shooting.gif?t=1737993568\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/Expansive_progression_paths_.png?t=1737993568\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equip yourself with the myriad spells from the <strong>5 Aspects</strong>. Each has its own theme and purpose in your arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you priorities the monopoly of Mana through <strong>Sorcery</strong>? Turn to the buffs and corpse manipulation prowess of <strong>Fleshsmithing</strong>? Or the many meta-effects that <strong>Conceptualism</strong> offers?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapt your build. Discover new firearms. <strong>Chamber your Rituals.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/Browsing_spells.gif?t=1737993568\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3183240?t=1737993568","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737993568","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/bc5007ea9ad0c212169af16a5866cd76eb3c8bc4/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737993568","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/bc5007ea9ad0c212169af16a5866cd76eb3c8bc4/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737993568","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"There is violent content in the fighting and killing of monsters during the player's exploration of the dungeons. There is also gore in the blood effects when monsters are killed."},"detailed_description":"<h1>Special gift for playtesters</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/RC_unique_revolver_banner.png?t=1737993568\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/High_octane_dark_fantasy_action_.png?t=1737993568\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture into the treacherous depths of Hell's Vestibule. Gun down the myriad monstrosities that populate Hell's corridors as you expand your repertoire. Master spells, sigils and firearms alike as you advance through this <strong>dark fantasy roguelike.</strong> \u2028</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/Flashy_gameplay.gif?t=1737993568\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183240/extras/Spellcasting_fused_with_gunplay_.png?t=1737993568\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlike typical action fantasy, your spells do not act standalone. Instead, spells empowers your firearm. Your bullets <strong>are your Spell's effects.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Empty magazines full of fire bolts, turn corpses to explosions, or engrave Rituals unto the ground. <strong>Tread the illimitable road of Ritualism.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img clas